                            <comment id="13019164" author="jeromatron" created="Wed, 13 Apr 2011 01:43:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching patch to make the udf context key specific to the keyspace and column family so it doesn&apos;t get overwritten.  Also changed the putNext case where the validation class is BytesType to use objToBB the way it should to handle things like Strings.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13019166" author="jeromatron" created="Wed, 13 Apr 2011 01:47:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Tested with basic row count pig script as well as multiple join/cogroup operations against multiple column families.  Tested input and output.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
